title: RAAF Record. Newsreel No. 02
creator_credit: Australia. Royal Australian Air Force. Directorate of Public Relations and Stanley Brogden
brief_description: The following newsreel items are covered: The end in Korea - No. 77 Squadron fought till the last day; Thanks sister! - RAAF evacuates Korean wounded; Canberras for RAAF - Australia makes jet bomber; The air race - London to New Zealand - 24 hours; Williamtown is busy - school of land/air warfare; Off to the coronation - RAAF and WRAAF looked fine; Faster than sound - RAAF gets sonic jet fighter. Narrated by Douglas H. Moon.
